        <h2>
            国语集解的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1061602">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1061602/" class="title-link">《国语》好的本子</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1061602"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1068752/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1068752/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">findlay</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-07-29"
      class="main-meta">2006-07-29 16:35:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1061602_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  熟悉颁布的人都清楚，读《国语》有几个好的本子，其中最好的一个就是《国语集解》。这本中华书局出版的《国语集解》由河北师范大学的两位著名的老师王树民和沈长云点校，王树民老师是中国史学史方面的大家，他的《中国史学史纲要》至今仍是很重要的参考书，沈长云老师是先秦史...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1061602/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1061602_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1061602_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
